Turns out `account.idTokenClaims?.tid` is undefined a LOT more than I thought, losing a lot of telemetry events.

I've changed this to `const tid = account.tenantId;` in https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/pull/260418 but we should probably bring this into a recovery release so that we can collect this data sooner rather than later.

